---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Black and White Wedding Invitations | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Elegant black and white wedding invitation suites with minimalist typography, timeless layouts, and modern wedding stationery design.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Black and White Wedding Invitations</h1>

    <p>
      Timeless, elegant, and effortlessly modern.
      Black and white wedding invitations remain one of the most sophisticated
      and versatile wedding stationery styles for modern couples.
    </p>

    <p>
      From minimalist typography to luxury editorial-inspired layouts,
      black and white wedding invitation suites create a refined aesthetic
      that works beautifully across classic, modern, formal, and contemporary weddings.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Timeless Wedding Stationery Design</h2>

    <p>
      Black and white wedding invitations have remained popular because they feel clean,
      elevated, and visually timeless. This style works especially well for luxury weddings,
      city weddings, modern venues, black tie celebrations, historic venues,
      and minimalist wedding aesthetics.
    </p>

    <p>
      Strong typography, thoughtful spacing, premium paper choices,
      and subtle design details allow black and white invitation suites
      to feel both understated and impactful.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular Black and White Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Minimalist wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Modern black tie wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Editorial-style wedding stationery</li>
      <li>Luxury monochrome invitation suites</li>
      <li>Classic serif typography invitations</li>
      <li>Modern script and serif combinations</li>
      <li>Contemporary black and white wedding designs</li>
      <li>Simple elegant wedding invitations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Elegant Wedding Invitation Suites</h2>

    <p>
      Our black and white wedding suites are designed to create a cohesive,
      elevated look throughout your wedding experience. Matching stationery options
      may include save the dates, invitation suites, RSVP cards, menus,
      welcome signs, seating charts, programs, and day-of details.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether your wedding style is classic, modern, luxury,
      editorial, or minimalist, black and white wedding invitations
      create a polished and timeless foundation for your celebration.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom Wedding Invitation Design</h2>

    <p>
      We also offer custom wedding invitation design services for couples
      looking for personalized layouts, custom typography, unique wording,
      and tailored wedding branding.
    </p>

    <p>
      Every wedding is different, and your stationery should reflect
      the personality and style of your celebration.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Are black and white wedding invitations still popular?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Black and white wedding invitations remain one of the most timeless
      and requested wedding stationery styles because they work across nearly every
      wedding aesthetic.
    </p>

    <h3>What wedding styles work best with black and white invitations?</h3>
    <p>
      Black tie weddings, luxury weddings, minimalist weddings,
      city weddings, modern weddings, and editorial-inspired weddings
      all pair beautifully with black and white stationery.
    </p>

    <h3>Can invitation suites be customized?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Typography, layouts, colors, paper styles, and wording can all be customized.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching signage and wedding day stationery?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching menus, signage, escort cards, programs,
      and other coordinated wedding paper goods are available.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
